Package: soilwaterptf
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2014-09-26
Title: Wosten et al. 1999 pedotransfer functions for soil hydraulic properties.
Author: Julien MOEYS <jules_m78-soiltexture@yahoo.fr>, with contributions from Till Francke <francke@uni-potsdam.de> (Rawls and Brakensiek PTFs)
Maintainer: Julien MOEYS <jules_m78-soiltexture@yahoo.fr> 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.1), soiltexture, soilwaterfun
Suggests: 
Description: Pedotransfer functions (PTFs) for estimating the physical parameters of soil 
    water retention and hydraulic conductivity functions from easily available soil 
    properties (typically soil texture, organic matter content, bulk density). The 
    pedotransfer function(s) implemeneted is (are): (1) Wosten et al. 1999 (Geoderma 
    90:169-185) pedotransfer functions for estimating the parameters of van-Genuchten (1980) 
    Mualem (1976) water retention and hydraulic conductivity functions (valid for European 
    soils).
License: AGPL-3
URL: http://soilwater.r-forge.r-project.org/ 
